  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK252">
<l>poruḷāṭci pōṟṟātārk killai yaruḷāṭci</l>
<l>yāṅkillai yūṉṟiṉ pavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As those possess no property who do not take care of it, so those possess no kindness who feed on flesh.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
